INSTRUCTIONS:
================================================================

This file contains the base64-encoded debug keystore for GitHub Actions.

TO ADD TO GITHUB SECRETS:

1. Copy the ENTIRE base64 string above (long line between the separator lines)
2. Go to: https://github.com/rafaelmeloreisnovo/BizHawkRafaelia/settings/secrets/actions
3. Click "New repository secret"
4. Name: ANDROID_KEYSTORE_BASE64
5. Value: Paste the base64 string
6. Click "Add secret"

AFTER ADDING THE SECRET:

- Delete this file from your local repository
- The GitHub Actions workflow will now sign APKs automatically

NOTE: This is a DEBUG keystore with public credentials.
      For production, generate a new keystore with strong passwords.

See MAINTAINER_README.md and APK_SIGNING_GUIDE.md for complete instructions.
